The paper deals with face recognition using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of coupled deep neural networks also suggests the involvement of machine learning (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of polarimetric thermal imaging, which could fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the paper also involves feature extraction and matching, which could fall under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
